_sText: The map's concept is that there is a small room divided into two areas, one is with the CT's and the other is the T's. in the middle of the room there's a ring and there are an entrance to it from each side of the room. the entrence immidietly closes when a player came inside the ring and it will open when he will die, so its a 1 on 1 knife tournament inside the ring.
